    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jan Eric Larsson</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:146px;\"><a href=\"http://www.goalart.com/aboutgoalart/janericlarsson.asp\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1/12/Janericlarsson.jpg\" width=\"144\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Janericlarsson.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jan Eric Larsson <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jan Eric Larsson</b>,<br />\na Swedish computer scientist, president, CEO, and founder of <i>GoalArt</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and professor of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_technology\">information technology</a> at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lund_University\">Lund University</a>, where he already obtained his Ph.D. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Automatic_control\">automatic control</a> in 1992. He was then <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postdoctoral_research\">postdoc</a> at <a href=\"/Stanford_University\" title=\"Stanford University\">Stanford University</a>. His research interests include applied <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, automatic control, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real-time_computing\">real-time</a> monitoring and diagnosis, multilevel flow modeling, and game playing. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Mobility\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mobility</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mobility\">Mobility</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Eric_Larsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Mobility\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In his 1987 note <i>Challenging that Mobility is Fundamental</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , Larsson questions <a href=\"/Dap_Hartmann\" title=\"Dap Hartmann\">Dap Hartmann's</a> definition of <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">mobility</a> based on <a href=\"/Legal_Move\" title=\"Legal Move\">legal</a> or <a href=\"/Pseudo-Legal_Move\" title=\"Pseudo-Legal Move\">pseudo-legal moves</a>, as well as distinct or total attacked squares <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nbut favors weighting of squares toward the <a href=\"/Center\" title=\"Center\">center</a> or the enemy king, safe mobility, and mobility based on <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">pawn structure</a> or even more complex second order computations.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Eric_Larsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a> (<b>1987</b>). <i>Challenging that Mobility is Fundamental</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#10_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal Vol. 10, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lup.lub.lu.se/search/publication/97d527c9-e7a2-4408-8fb5-0b63a5991871\">Knowledge-Based Methods for Control Systems</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lund_University\">Lund University</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=179767\">Diagnostic Reasoning Strategies for Means-End Models</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Automatica\">Automatica</a>, Vol. 30, No. 5, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.goalart.com/publications/1994-Automatica-JE.pdf\">pdf preprint</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Understanding the Turing Test</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#34_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 34, No. 1</a>, on <a href=\"/Maarten_van_Emden\" title=\"Maarten van Emden\">Maarten van Emden</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Andr%C3%A9_Vellino&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"André Vellino (page does not exist)\">André Vellino</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>From Chinese Room to Human Window</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#33_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 33, No. 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Eric_Larsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/M3z_ygsx9W4/_5zcI78-szkJ\">Speed of chess programs?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 29, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/b-LPW2cvbSU/X7c__HhVXh8J\">0x88?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 31, 1995&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/KqoFQQXxRF4/IGZXBGT8S_4J\">Testing Chess Programs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 09, 1996</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/4fk13QkqIoQ/jqiTuXogL-0J\">Re: Deep Blue against Kasparov</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 02, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/su1X8FrRMPA/dMUBRY-RT4AJ\">xboard/winboard interface documentation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, November 27, 1998</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Eric_Larsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jan-eric-larsson-4b561b5a/\">Jan Eric Larsson | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.goalart.com/aboutgoalart/janericlarsson.asp\">GoalArt: Jan Eric Larsson</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dhf.se/keypeople.html\">DHF Airport Systems - Keypeople</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Eric_Larsson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.goalart.com/aboutgoalart/janericlarsson.asp\">GoalArt: Jan Eric Larsson</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.goalart.com/\">GoalArt</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jan Eric Larsson</a> (<b>1987</b>). <i>Challenging that Mobility is Fundamental</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#10_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 10, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Dap_Hartmann\" title=\"Dap Hartmann\">Dap Hartmann</a> (<b>1987</b>). <i>How to Extract Relevant Knowledge from Grandmaster Games. Part 2: the Notion of Mobility, and the Work of <a href=\"/Adriaan_de_Groot\" title=\"Adriaan de Groot\">De Groot</a> and <a href=\"/Eliot_Slater\" title=\"Eliot Slater\">Slater</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#10_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 10, No. 2</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lup.lub.lu.se/search/person/it-jla\">Jan Eric Larsson - Lund University Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_room\">Chinese room from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.or